```text
score(tech) =
  α * Σ SUPPORTS.weight*decay
- β * Σ CONTRADICTS.weight*decay
+ γ * Σ ADDRESSES(Requirement).weight
- δ * Σ VIOLATES(Constraint).severity
+ ε * org_utilization(OWNED_BY team skill/experience)
+ ζ * inverse(Incident linkage risk)
```

- Coefficients α..ζ are domain-tunable (service/security/data presets).

